snippet.title: ROBOCRAFT 2 - Hidden Weapon Bot By FilthyShrooms
snippet.description:
https://www.robocraft2.com

Over the weekend during an online battle test, community member FilthyShrooms took to the battlefield with this creation which uses logic and physics joints to create a hidden weapon!
